Mofina is priest found on the top floor of the Arceuus church. Players who speak to her will learn that the Arceuus church is used for meditation for the mysteries of the Dark Altar, rather than a church used for worshipping gods. However, players may pray at the altar to restore their prayer points.

In addition, she will also explain how the Citizens of Arceuus appear spiritual and inhuman. Through the power of the Dark Altar, they are able to achieve immortality by moving their soul from their mortal body into a corporeal one. Their souls are freed from the mortal bodies in the crypt below the church, and take on the incorporeal form commonly seen among Arceuus residents.

Mofina was one of the party guests invited by Duke Horacio to the party during the 2021 Birthday event.
